message.content: The most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as the paper deals with natural language processing and information retrieval. Other likely sub-categories could be "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval), "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence), "cs.LG" (Machine Learning), and "cs.DL" (Deep Learning) as these fields are closely related to the topic of the paper.
